stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending : Dataset record created\n(POST /datasets/initiate-upload)

    pending --> uploaded : Raw file PUT to R2\n+ POST /complete-upload

    uploaded --> harmonizing : Worker claims job\n(claim_next_job RPC)\njob_type = harmonization

    harmonizing --> tiling : Harmonization complete\nharmonized .laz written to R2

    tiling --> ready : COPC written to R2\ndatasets.copc_url updated

    ready --> processing_assets : User triggers\nPOST /datasets/{id}/extract-road-assets\njob_type = road_assets

    ready --> processing_bim : User triggers\nPOST /datasets/{id}/extract-bim\njob_type = bim_extraction

    processing_assets --> ready : road_assets_url + features\nwritten back to datasets

    processing_bim --> ready : ifc_url + dxf_url + features\nwritten back to datasets

    harmonizing --> failed : Worker error\nerror_message recorded

    tiling --> failed : Worker error\nerror_message recorded

    processing_assets --> failed : Worker error

    processing_bim --> failed : Worker error

    failed --> uploaded : User retries\n(POST /datasets/{id}/retry)

    ready --> [*] : Dataset deleted\n(CASCADE removes all children)

    note right of harmonizing
        processing_jobs.status transitions:
        queued → processing → completed / failed
        progress: 0 → 100 (realtime via Supabase)
    end note

    note right of ready
        datasets.status = "ready"
        Viewer can now stream COPC
        AI agent can now query features
    end note
